text: James W. Edming is an American politician and businessman. From Glen Flora, Wisconsin, Edming owns Edming Oil Company. He also owned pizza and manufacturing companies. Edming is a Republican. He also served on the Rusk County, Wisconsin Board of Supervisors.Wisconsin Vote.org.-James W.
